      <title>Pop Mart，Haidilao，Nongfu Spring为中国的消费定下基调</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/pop-mart-haidilao-nongfu-spring-to-set-tone-for-china-consumption</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在一项调查显示消费者感到越来越乐观和北京概述了通过促进收入来恢复消费的计划后，中国消费者巨头在下周的收入中占主导地位。]]></description>
